It takes teachers from the rural depths so much time to fumble and fill out and submit the Tpad online to their employer.Those that do not fill out and submit this thing are faced with many threats, including warning letters or withholding of their salaries. Anyone who has ‘sampled’ police cells will admit that they all smell the same. There is a municipal smell in all stations and how that comes to be we cannot tell. It is the same with teachers, especially those based in rural areas. They somehow look the same and cannot hide the profession from the people around them.



